    <title>Latex的学习（1）</title>
    <link href="https://neverlandsx.github.io/2021/01/10/Latex%20study1/"/>
    <id>https://neverlandsx.github.io/2021/01/10/Latex%20study1/</id>
    <published>2021-01-09T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-01-10T16:01:02.486Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<pre><code>对Latex的学习主要参考了刘海洋的《Latex入门》，下面将用勾股定理的pdf进行实操。使用的软件是Visual Studio Code,通过LaTeX Workshop 插件来实现Latex。</code></pre><a id="more"></a><figure class="highlight livescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">\documentclass[UTF8]&#123;ctexart&#125;</span>                %当命令的参数为可选参数时为[];否者为&#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\newtheorem&#123;theorem&#125;&#123;Theorem&#125;</span>                %提供theorem所需环境</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\usepackage&#123;graphicx&#125;</span>                       %提供插入图片所需的宏包</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\usepackage&#123;float&#125;</span>                          %提供不浮动table（表格）</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\usepackage&#123;amsmath&#125;</span>                        %提供eqref所需环境</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\usepackage&#123;geometry&#125;</span>                       %该包用于设计页面尺寸</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\geometry&#123;a6paper,centering,scale=0.8&#125;</span>      %纸张A6大小，版心居中，长宽占页面的<span class="number">0.8</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\usepackage[format=hang,font=small,textfont=it]&#123;caption&#125;</span>        %标题悬挂对齐（即编号向左突出），整体用小字号，标题文本用斜体（英文）/楷书（汉字）</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\usepackage[nottoc]&#123;tocbibind&#125;</span>              %在目录中加入包括目录，参考文献的所有标题，nottoc取消目录本身</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\newcommand\degree&#123;^\circ&#125;</span>                %将命令^<span class="string">\circle用简单的degree代替</span></span><br><span class="line">%------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\title&#123;</span> <span class="string">\heiti</span> 杂谈勾股定理&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\author&#123;</span> <span class="string">\kaishu</span> Zhangsan<span class="string">\\Peking&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\date&#123;\today&#125;</span>                                % <span class="string">\today</span> 输出的是电脑的当日的时期</span><br><span class="line">%以上信息仅是对文章信息提前申明，得通过<span class="string">\maketitle输出，maketitle的输出格式是固定的</span></span><br><span class="line">%  <span class="regexp">/是转义字符；/</span>/为换行</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\bibliographystyle&#123;plain&#125;</span>                     % <span class="string">\bibliographystyle</span> 声明参考文献格式</span><br><span class="line">% <span class="string">\begin</span> 以上部分都称为导言区（premble）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">%<span class="string">\begin</span> 与 <span class="string">\end</span> 之间为pdf的输出内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\begin&#123;document&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\maketitle</span>                                     %输出文章信息(前文定义的)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\begin&#123;abstract&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">    这是一篇勾股定理的小短文。                   %摘要在abstract环境中生成</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\end&#123;abstract&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\tableofcontents</span>                               %输出目录</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\section&#123;勾股定理在古代&#125;</span>                           %开始新一节,自动排序</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">西方称勾股定理为毕达哥拉斯定理 <span class="string">\cite&#123;Kline&#125;，将其发</span>  现归功于公元前 <span class="number">6</span> 世纪的毕达哥拉斯学派。该定理的严格证明见于欧几里德</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\footnote&#123;欧几里得，约公元前</span> <span class="number">330</span>--<span class="number">275</span> 年。&#125; 的《几何原本》的命题 <span class="number">47</span>。   </span><br><span class="line">%数字前后加空格，汉字前后的空格等于没有；段前无需缩进，自动缩进；中间空出一行，代表分段。</span><br><span class="line">%<span class="string">&#x27; \footnote&#123;&#125; &#x27;</span>为脚注命令，花括号内为脚注内容</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">我国《周髀算经》载商高（约公元前 <span class="number">12</span> 世纪）答周公问：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\begin&#123;quote&#125;</span>                                     %使用quote环境进行引用以突出引用内容</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">\zihao&#123;-5&#125;\kaishu</span> 勾广三，股修四，径隅五。      % <span class="string">&#x27;\zihao&#123;-5&#125;&#x27;</span> 为小<span class="number">5</span>号;<span class="string">&#x27;\kaishu&#x27;</span> 为楷书</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\end&#123;quote&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">又载陈子（约公元前 <span class="number">7</span>--<span class="number">6</span> 世纪）答问：……              %<span class="string">&#x27;--&#x27;</span>表示一个宽度与n相当的短划线</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">图<span class="string">\ref&#123;fig:xiantu&#125;是我国古代对勾股定理的一种证明</span> <span class="string">\cite&#123;quanjing&#125;。</span>          %通过<span class="string">\ref&#123;&#125;自动显示图的序号</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\begin&#123;figure&#125;[ht]</span>                                      %figure是指图片可以自适应浮动的环境吗，ht表示可以出现页面顶部和底部</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">\centering</span>                                          %<span class="string">&#x27;\centering&#x27;</span> 表示后面内容居中</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">\includegraphics[width=3cm]&#123;xian.jpeg&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">\caption&#123;宋赵爽在《周髀算经》注中所做的弦图，给出了一个极具对称美的证明。&#125;</span>          %<span class="string">&#x27;\caption&#123;&#125;&#x27;</span> 能给出标题，并自动编号</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">\label&#123;fig:xiantu&#125;</span>                                  %定义一个标签，以便方便引用</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\end&#123;figure&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\section&#123;勾股定理的近代形式&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\begin&#123;theorem&#125;[勾股定理]</span>                        %使用theorem环境来写定理</span><br><span class="line">    直角三角形斜边的平方等于两腰的平方和。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    可以用符号语言表述为：设直角三角形$ABC$ ,其中<span class="string">\angle</span> C= $<span class="number">90</span><span class="string">\degree$</span> ,则有         % $内容$ 表示里面的内容用公式格式，被称为行内公式</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">\begin&#123;equation&#125;\label&#123;eq:gougu&#125;</span>                                            %用label定义公式标签方便提及公式</span><br><span class="line">        AB^<span class="number">2</span>=BC^<span class="number">2</span>+AC^<span class="number">2.</span>                                                         %采用了equation 环境，此种为列表公式</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">\end&#123;equation&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\end&#123;theorem&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">满足式 <span class="string">\eqref&#123;eq:gougu&#125;</span> 的整数称为<span class="string">\emph&#123;勾股数&#125;，下表列出了一些较小的勾股数：</span>                   %<span class="string">&#x27;\emph&#123;&#125;&#x27;</span> 表强调，通过<span class="string">\eqref&#123;&#125;自动显示公式序号</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\begin&#123;table&#125;[H]</span>                                        %table提供的是浮动表格环境，但[H]使其固定</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\begin&#123;tabular&#125;&#123;|rrr|&#125;</span>                                  %tabular提供制表环境，<span class="string">&#x27;|rrr|&#x27;</span>示右对齐,有三列，表格两侧有两条竖线</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">\hline</span></span><br><span class="line">    直角边 $a$ &amp; 直角边 $b$ &amp; 斜边 $c$ <span class="string">\\</span>                   %<span class="string">&#x27;\hline&#x27;</span>表示画出一条横线；<span class="string">\\表示换行；列之间用&amp;隔开</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">\hline</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="number">3</span> &amp; <span class="number">4</span> &amp; <span class="number">5</span> <span class="string">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="number">5</span> &amp; <span class="number">12</span> &amp; <span class="number">13</span> <span class="string">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">\hline</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\end&#123;tabular&#125;%</span>                                          %<span class="string">&#x27;%&#x27;</span>取消换行</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\qquad</span>                                                  %产生两个M宽度的间隔</span><br><span class="line">($a^<span class="number">2</span> + b^<span class="number">2</span> = c^<span class="number">2</span>$)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\end&#123;table&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\nocite&#123;Shiye&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\bibliography&#123;math&#125;</span>                                       %从文献数据库math(该数据库通过JabRef软件得到)中获取文献信息，输出的.bib文件放在相同目录中</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\end&#123;document&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编译需选择下图中圈出的选项：</p><img src="/2021/01/10/Latex%20study1/%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91.jpg" class title="编译"><p><strong>这就是完成后的效果！</strong></p><img src="/2021/01/10/Latex%20study1/%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E5%9B%BE.jpg" class title="效果图">]]></content>
    
    
